            "id": "/data/2017/08/15/usmap-v0-2-1/",
            "title": "usmap v0.2.1 released"
            "content_html": "<p><code class=\"highlighter-rouge\">usmap v0.2.1</code> is now available for download on <a href=\"https://cran.r-project.org/package=usmap\">CRAN</a>. This minor update includes bug fixes and documentation improvements.</p>\n\n<p>You can read the full changelog <a href=\"https://github.com/pdil/usmap/releases/tag/v0.2.1\">here</a>.</p>",
